text: Dried fruits are very tasty. Particularly nice was their buckwheat chips, which were very crispy and airy. Staff were also friendly, offering samples for all the displayed items. Great place to shop for snacks overall.
Service is good. But this biscuit really not nice. Flour taste very strong. No wonder no tasting. Have to buy 4 instead of one. U ruin ur reputation by selling such biscuit.
Bought their sesame balls and yogurt cubes. Both were nice but the yogurt cubes were a little too sweet. Service was very good!
Great taste. Unlikely other dried fruits, love the slightly sweet dried strawberries and overall the snacks are delicious! Changed my perception of Chinese snacks, good quality!
It's good but the queue a bit long so will try again to purchase the next time
